<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Library Management System</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-sRIl4kxILFvY47J16cr9ZwB07vP4J8+LH7qKQnuqkuIAvNWLzeN8tE5YBujZqJLB" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/7.0.0/css/all.min.css" integrity="sha512-DxV+EoADOkOygM4IR9yXP8Sb2qwgidEmeqAEmDKIOfPRQZOWbXCzLC6vjbZyy0vPisbH2SyW27+ddLVCN+OMzQ==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />

    <style>

        .image {
            height: 100vh;
        }

        .anc {
            transition: all 0.5s ease;
            background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);
            color: black;
        }

            .anc:hover {
                transform: translateY(-20px);
                box-shadow: 0px 0px 0px rgb(230, 229, 229);
                background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);
                color: rgb(0, 0, 0);
            }

        .img-m {
            height: 12rem;
        }

        .login {
            animation: shadow 1s ease infinite;
        }

        .main {
            background: url(https://i.pinimg.com/736x/12/9a/32/129a32142a1dd468c490f81d989c5cd1.jpg);
            backdrop-filter: opacity(0.5);
        }






        /* From Uiverse.io by Madflows */
        .button {
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            height: 3rem;
            padding: 0 2rem;
            border-radius: 1.5rem;
            background: #3d3a4e;
            background-size: 400%;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

            .button:hover::before {
                transform: scaleX(1);
            }

        .button-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .button::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            transform: scaleX(0);
            transform-origin: 0 50%;
            width: 100%;
            height: inherit;
            border-radius: inherit;
            background: linear-gradient( 82.3deg, rgba(150, 93, 233, 1) 10.8%, rgba(99, 88, 238, 1) 94.3% );
            transition: all 0.475s;
        }

    </style>

</head>
<body>
    <div class="container-fluid">

        <div class="row main">
            <div class="col-sm-5 bg-dark bg-opacity-75 text-white text-center p-5 fs-3 justify-content-center d-flex align-items-center gap-5 flex-column flex-wrap py-1" style="height: 100vh;">
                A library is a collection of sources of information and similar resources, made accessible to a defined community for reference or borrowing. It provides physical and digital access to material.   Sidney Sheldon perfectly describes: <i>“Libraries store the energy that fuels the imagination. They open up windows to the world and inspire us to explore and achieve, and contribute to improving our quality of life.”</i>



            </div>
            <div class="text-white d-flex  bg-dark bg-opacity-75 justify-content-center align-items-center image  overflow-hidden p-0 col-sm-7"
                 ">
                <div class="brand d-flex flex-column align-items-center w-75 gap-2">
                    <img src="https://img.freepik.com/premium-vector/vector-design-ebook-reader-icon-style_1250006-23027.jpg" class="img-m rounded-circle" />
                    <h1 class="m-0 p-0 fw-bold" style="font-family:Georgia, 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;">RiskFlight</h1>
                    <p class="m-0 fs-4" style="font-family:Verdana, Geneva, Tahoma, sans-serif;">Library</p>

                    <a class="text-decoration-none text-white" asp-action="librarianLogin">
                        <button class="button mt-5">
                            <span class="button-content fw-bold fs-5">Librarian Login</span>
                        </button>
                    </a>




                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-FKyoEForCGlyvwx9Hj09JcYn3nv7wiPVlz7YYwJrWVcXK/BmnVDxM+D2scQbITxI" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script>
        function myFunction() {
        var x = document.getElementById("pass");
        if (x.type === "password") {
            x.type = "text";
        } else {
            x.type = "password";
        }
        }
    </script>

    <script src="./script.js">


    </script>
    <script src="./script.js">




    </script>
</body>
</html>